mpanies the fund looks for stock where the price is low relative to the underlying value of the company and its real estate  fund symbol soaix the income fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing under usual circumstances at least  of its assets in a portfolio of taxable municipal bonds income producing convertible securities preferred stock high yield us corporate bonds and collateralized mortgage obligations the income fund may also invest in us government agency securities fund symbol soamx the municipal tax free bond fund seeks to achieve its investment objectives by investing under usual circumstances at least  of its assets in municipal bonds fund symbol soaox the income and opportunity fund has the flexibility to invest in the following securities to best achieve the objective of providing shareholders with the potential for both income and growth equity securities including common stock preferred stock and convertible preferred stock fixed income securities including taxable municipal bonds corporate bonds and cmos real estate investment trusts reits including equity and mortgage reits master limited partnerships mlps   fund symbol soavx the value fund focuses on the large cap value segment of the us equity market the value fund invests at least  of its total assets in large cap equity securities of companies in the value segment of the market using the “value” approach the adviser buys for the value fund those securities considered to be conservatively valued relative to the securities of comparable companies to earn current income the value fund will invest in the equity securities of companies that have a proven history of paying consistent dividends the value fund may also invest in mlps fund symbol soaex the energy fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing at least  of its assets in energy and energy related companies exploration production and transmission of energy or energy fuels the fund will invest in master limited partnerships mlps that derive the majority of their revenue from energy infrastructure assets and energy related assets or activities including businesses making or servicing of products for energy related activities energy research energy conservation find an investment counselor visit the spirit of america investment fund website there are risks inherent in investing  spirit of america mutual funds are offered by prospectus only investors are advised to consider the fund’s investment objectives risks charges and expenses before investing the prospectus contains this and other information about the investment company read the prospectus carefully before you invest or send money the information in this website is for us and us virgin islands residents only the spirit of america funds described in this website are registered only in the united states and the information on this website does not constitute an offer to sell or a solicitation of an offer to purchase the spirit of america funds outside of the united states and us virgin islands the shares of spirit of america funds are not insured by the fdic or any other agency and involve investment risks including the possible loss of the principal amount invested spirit of america funds are distributed exclusively by david lerner associates inc before investing in any of the spirit of america funds investors should carefully read prospectuses and summary prospectuses if any in addition investors should consider a funds investment objectives risks charges and expenses fund prospectuses and summary prospectuses if any contain this and other information about the funds and may be obtained by contacting your investment counselor viewing on the spirit of america fund’s site or calling  or by mail spirit of america management corp  jericho turnpike po box  syosset ny   for complete information regarding performance data current to the most recent month end and to obtain a prospectus contact david lerner associates inc 